# Bazaar frontend env. Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# Deployed Bazaar subgraph GraphQL endpoint (e.g. a self-hosted graph-node behind
# HTTPS, or http://localhost:8000/subgraphs/name/bazaar for a local node). When
# unset, the UI reads everything from the chain directly (match history / P&L are
# hidden). See indexer/README.md "Self-host on a VPS" for the deployment.
VITE_SUBGRAPH_URL=
